01:26:06.428 --> 01:26:09.796
Where you going?

01:26:14.836 --> 01:26:16.570
Hold it right there.

01:26:16.572 --> 01:26:18.472
Hey, watch yourselves.

01:26:18.474 --> 01:26:20.307
