who he claims to be.

01:26:34.356 --> 01:26:35.522
Oh, really?

01:26:35.524 --> 01:26:37.391
Rayburn, take him downtown.

01:26:37.393 --> 01:26:38.892
You got it, sheriff.

01:26:40.828 --> 01:26:42.696
